column1: GoFreight Page Ranking Comparison: Jan-Jun 2025 vs Dec 2025

1. MASSIVE TRAFFIC DROP: Homepage dropped from 6
2. ARCHIVE SUBDOMAIN ISSUE: Most Dec 2025 top pages are on archive.gofreight.com instead of www.gofreight.com
3. DDP INCOTERMS PAGE DISAPPEARED: Was #2 with 4
4. STANDARD CARRIER ALPHA CODE DISAPPEARED: Was #3 with 2
5. NEW SUPPORT PAGES APPEARING: support.gofreight.com pages now ranking (bond status
RECOMMENDATION: Implement 301 redirects from archive subdomain to www domain to consolidate traffic
